Very simple example using Symmetric Encryption 
using Stream-Oriented or Stream-Cipher algorithms.
This is just to now how to use easily steram-oriented ciphers in 
JAVA (JCE)

Of course  there are many different stream-ciphers (algorithms).
Some of them:

RC4 (Sometimes appearing as ARC or ARCFOUR)
CHACHA-20

SALSA-20
RABBIT
A5 Family (A5/1, A5/2)
A8
VEST
TRIVIUM

